{"word":"βλῆμα","slug":"βλῆμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βλῆμα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βάλλω'><el>βάλλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a throw, cast</i>, of dice, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a shot, wound</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>a coverlet</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}